Reasoning: The paper discusses the development of a web portal software for data management in biomedical research projects. The paper focuses on functional and quality requirements for data management, and introduces a modular web portal software called menoci. The paper also discusses the need for an ecosystem of open source software tools to support the structural transformation process of research data management. Based on these topics, the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories are cs.DL (Digital Libraries), cs.CY (Computers and Society), cs.CR (Cryptography and Security), cs.DB (Databases), and cs.IR (Information Retrieval).
